To encourage law students of Baze University towards their journey as future lawyers, Managing Partner of Principle Legal Consult, Barr. Prada Uzodimma has urged the students to apply for her scholarship grant. According to her, the Prada Uzodimma Law School scholarship grant is part of the corporate social responsibility of Principle Legal Consult. She advised the law students of Baze University to apply for the scholarship grant and use it as a tool towards achieving their future goals of being called to the Nigerian Bar. Uzodimma also encouraged the students to put their foot forward in preparation for their final exams and stand out as an exemplary figure and role model to the law students.